# xFusionCorp Industries - Machine Learning Environment Setup

## Day 1: Python Virtual Environment Setup

### Project Overview

This project documents the initial setup of a standardized Python development environment for the **xFusionCorp Industries Machine Learning Team**.

The objective of this task is to create an isolated Python environment where machine learning models can be developed, tested, and deployed without affecting the system-wide Python installation.

